Subject: [PATCH 46/53] web-app: chat export analytics event

Fire a 'chat_export' analytics event when a chat is successfully
exported (via window.__slothfulTrack). The 'custom_range' property
indicates whether the user filled in a From or Until date in the
confirm dialog. No-op on other targets and when analytics is
disabled.

